          "name": "29bb",
          "text": "Dear Friends,",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "95cf49dd0fea_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "c2c7",
          "text": "One of the major insights I gained while helping birth the Cultural Evolution Society was that people don’t even know this field of research exists. And yet, as I began to follow the publication of scholarly work from more than 2000 scholars and practitioners as they joined the society, I realized that even the most educated among them cannot see how large and dynamic this field truly is.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 85,
              "href": "https://culturalevolutionsociety.org/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 59,
              "title": "",
